lead_paragraph: Peyton Manning wanted to make one thing perfectly clear when he arrived in the Golden Gate City for the golden anniversary of the Super Bowl: "Our defense is what got us here."

headline.print_headline: Denver Brings Dominant Defense Into Super Bowl 50
